    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This specification provides IPv6 extensions to the Mobile IPv4 protocol.  The extensions allow a dual-stack node to use IPv4 and IPv6 home addresses as well as to move between IPv4 and dual stack network infrastructures. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
